# Antigravity Lead Machine — Architecture Overview

This document provides a detailed technical architecture of the **Antigravity Lead Machine**, an automated lead generation system designed to discover businesses without websites and manage them via a lightweight CRM and AI-powered Telegram interface.

---

## 1. High-Level Architecture

The system operates on an orchestrated serverless/self-hosted architecture that relies on **n8n** for workflow automation, **Google Sheets** for database and state management, **SerpApi** for data acquisition, and **OpenClaw AI / Telegram** for user interaction.

